ists/Justice">Justice</a>等乐队一起表演。</p><p>明年夏天，他们还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796">在巴塞罗那的 Primavera Sound 演出</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/khruangbin-announce-biggest-headline-show-gunnersbury-park-tv-on-the-radio-buy-tickets-3800167">在伦敦 Gunnersbury 公园的大型户外演出中为 Khruangbin 提供支持</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftv-on-the-radio-tickets%2Fartist%2F904793" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tv-on-the-radios-tunde-adebimpe-is-on-the-cast-of-star-wars-skeleton-crew-ive-been-about-it-since-82-3818629">TV On The Radio 的 Tunde Adebimpe 加入了《星球大战：骷髅船员》的演员阵容：“自 82 年以来我就一直关注这个问题”，该剧</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
