罗尼·拉德克 (Ronnie Radke) 因入狱被拒签证入境，英国巡演取消https://www.nme.com/news/music/falling-in-reverse-uk-tour-cancelled-as-ronnie-radke-denied-visa-entry-due-to-prison-time-3818592?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=因罗尼·拉德克因入狱而被拒绝签证入境而陷入反向英国巡演被取消Daniel PetersWed, 04 Dec 2024 09:23:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3818592 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="倒退" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> 2008 年，拉德克因 2006 年发生的一场致命争吵而入狱一年多</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/falling-in-reverse-uk-tour-cancelled-as-ronnie-radke-denied-visa-entry-due-to-prison-time-3818592">由于 Ronnie Radke 因入狱而被拒绝签证入境，《Falling in Reverse》英国巡演被取消，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="倒退" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/FallingInReverse-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/falling-in-reverse">Falling In Reverse</a>宣布取消他们的英国巡演，因为主唱罗尼·拉德克 (Ronnie Radke) 据称因在监狱服刑而被拒绝签证入境。</p><p>这支金属核乐队的<em>“Popular Monstour 2: World Domination”</em>巡演定于今天（12 月 4 日）在英国曼彻斯特举行。然而，乐队昨天在 Instagram Story 中宣布，他们将不再按计划进行。</p><p> “我们遗憾地宣布，内政部已拒绝 Ronnie 参加 2024 年剩余英国演出的签证申请，”声明中写道。巡演计划于 12 月 16 日在伦敦 The O2 结束。</p><p> “英国目前拒绝入狱超过 12 个月的签证申请人入境，就像 Ronnie 在 2008 年所做的那样。”据<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/grounds-for-refusal-criminality/grounds-for-refusal-criminality-accessible#:~:text=Sentences%20of%2012%20months%20or,you%20must%20refuse%20their%20application." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Gov.uk</em></a>称，“在英国或海外被判犯有刑事罪”并服刑“至少 12 个月或更长时间”的申请人将被拒绝签证申请。</p><p>乐队补充说，《 <em>Popular Monstour 2》的</em>演出将推迟到明年，“同时我们将继续合法地解决这个问题，以获得必要的签证”。持票人现在可以从购买点退款。 </p><figure id="attachment_3786097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3786097" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3786097" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live.jpg" alt="罗尼·拉德克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Ronnie-Radke-Live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3786097" class="wp-caption-text">罗尼·拉德克.图片来源：丹尼尔·奈顿/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/falling-in-reverse-cancel-u-k-tour-ronnie-radke-visa-denied-1235844232/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard 报道</em></a>，2006 年内华达州发生的一场争吵导致 18 岁的迈克尔·库克 (Michael Cook) 死亡，拉德克因此被判缓刑，他参与了打斗，但并未直接参与致命行为。然而，两年后，拉德克违反了缓刑规定，被判入狱一年多。</p><p>巡演原定在英国之前先到达欧洲，但由于“与制作相关的后勤问题”，后半段日期被取消。该乐队预计将于<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCvyK1Bv4v-/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2025 年 3 月在澳大利亚</a>举行演出。</p><p>八月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-veil-brides-andy-biersack-defends-supporting-falling-in-reverse-and-ronnie-radke-friendship-3788881"><em>《Popular Monstour 2》</em>的开场黑面纱新娘为他们选择与拉德克一起巡演进行了辩护</a>，拉德克此前曾面临虐待、强奸、攻击和跨性别者恐惧症的指控，但他一直否认所有这些指控。</p><p>其中一些指控在音乐评论家安东尼·凡塔诺 (Anthony Fantano) 2023 年的一段视频中得到了回应， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/falling-in-reverses-ronnie-radke-reportedly-files-defamation-suit-against-anthony-fantano-3786095">今年 8 月，拉德克 (Radke) 向安东尼·凡塔诺 (Anthony Fantano) 提起了诽谤诉讼</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/falling-in-reverse-uk-tour-cancelled-as-ronnie-radke-denied-visa-entry-due-to-prison-time-3818592">由于 Ronnie Radke 因入狱而被拒绝签证入境，《Falling in Reverse》英国巡演被取消，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
